{"body": "Lowering BCrypt cost might be useful in test environment where you don't care about password security but do care about speed. I already do this in test_helper:\r\n\r\n    require \"bcrypt\"\r\n    silence_warnings do\r\n      BCrypt::Engine::DEFAULT_COST = BCrypt::Engine::MIN_COST\r\n    end\r\n\r\n(Gives a free 4 second boost in my case.) But I think this could be done by default.\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2482862", "created_at": "2011-10-21T15:52:35Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/285#issuecomment-2482862", "updated_at": "2011-10-21T15:52:35Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 285, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/semaperepelitsa", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/607564f1a15f1899c71b4a9fdfc33ac2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fdfaa83a66fe63d7e6e744189e2594a31.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/received_events", "gravatar_id": "607564f1a15f1899c71b4a9fdfc33ac2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "semaperepelitsa", "type": "User", "id": 347921, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/semaperepelitsa/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238635abd3543c1510124c0"}, "id": 2482862, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/285"}
